branchCategory.name: C(D)QSK, Compact Cylinder, Double Acting, Single Rod, Non-rotating
branchCategory.description: <p>The CQSK single non-rotating rod, double acting version of the compact cylinder is available for those small bore cylinder applications where saving space is a concern. The CQSK offers standard strokes up to 50mm. Both switch capable and non-switch capable body styles are the same, and switches can be mounted on three (12-16 bore) and four (20-25 bore) sides.</p>
